wikipedia_page.main: Leonard George Butt (26 August 1910 in Wilmslow – June 1994) was a professional footballer, who played for Stockport County, Macclesfield Town, Huddersfield Town, Blackburn Rovers, York City and Mansfield Town.He was later manager at Mossley  and Macclesfield Town.
